Subject: [PATCH 3/4] render: gles2: Support EGL_WL_bind_wayland_display
 extension

See:
https://registry.khronos.org/EGL/extensions/WL/EGL_WL_bind_wayland_display.txt

Signed-off-by: Jeffy Chen <jeffy.chen@rock-chips.com>
